feat: bulk download as ZIP archive instead of multiple window.open

Add POST /api/files/download-archive endpoint that streams a ZIP file
using the archiver package, fetching each file from S3 and piping into
the archive. Handles duplicate filenames with (N) suffix.

Replace broken bulk download (window.open loop blocked by browsers)
with handleBulkDownload that requests the archive, shows a loading
toast, and triggers a single file download. Single file downloads now
use <a> click instead of window.open for reliability.
